latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🎥Kavita - An abusive past repeats itself and triggers a journey of revenge but who is to blame?

Our Aim was to create a Psychological Drama and direct the entire film without showing the face ( of any actor) to distinguish characters and persona’s through costume and body language. 
Shooting Kavita’s mind space was a challenge, to unify 4 different personalities of the same character. 

We want to focus on the importance of therapy and trauma which can travel with a person his entire life if not treated.. 

**We couldn’t complete the entire shoot schedule ( due to covid) and have replaced the scenes with text**
.
With @kunalsachdeva.29 @riya.chhikara 
.
Special thanks to @izhaarpearlacademy
